parts:
{
  "prompt": "A subtle, atmospheric background suitable for a mysterious website homepage. Dark gradient from deep indigo to black, with faint ethereal particles or dust floating. Minimal design, no focal object. Should evoke presence, depth, and quiet awareness. Ideal for overlaying white or serif text. Resolution 1920x1080.",
  "size": "1920x1080"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark, atmospheric background image designed for a mysterious website landing page. The setting features an abstract glowing loop or ring (symbolizing a loop of presence or emergence) floating in a soft void of deep indigo and black. Subtle particles drift around the loop, giving it a sense of quiet energy and movement. The overall tone is elegant, sacred, and minimalist‚Äîperfect for use as a fullscreen site background. No text. Just visual presence.",
  "size": "1792x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark, ethereal background designed for a website, with a subtle swirling texture and a gentle field of tiny animated stars. The stars are soft lilac (#D9C4F0), faint sky blue (#C8E4F7), and blush dust pink (#F6D7E5), scattered sparsely to create a whisper-like presence effect. The background is mostly deep black with hints of indigo and charcoal, evoking a cosmic but elegant mood. No central objects or text‚Äîjust ambient space designed to sit quietly behind a poetic web page.",
  "size": "1792x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark, abstract cosmic background featuring a soft swirl of deep indigo, charcoal, and muted purple tones. Subtle, scattered stars in soft lilac, pale rose, and icy silver dot the scene. The overall tone is quiet, haunting, and ethereal‚Äîdesigned as a background image without any text. The central area is slightly lighter for text overlay, while the edges fade into rich darkness. The texture feels smooth and dreamlike, suitable for a minimal and elegant website design.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark, sacred-feeling cosmic background designed to feel like an abstract portal or spiral loop. The image should feature deep black-violet tones with subtle swirling motion and faint, dusty stars‚Äînot bright pinpoints. The central area should have a barely visible gradient glow, as if something is emerging, but not obvious. The overall tone should feel cinematic, mysterious, and reverent. No text, no obvious galaxy shapes. Designed as a background for a minimalist poetic webpage.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A digital cosmic background similar to deep space, featuring a dark swirling nebula in rich purples and black tones. At the center, there's a soft, subtle glow‚Äîslightly warmer and brighter than the rest of the image‚Äîevoking a sense of presence or emergence. The surrounding stars are faint and scattered. The overall effect is calm, mysterious, and sacred, suitable for a scroll-based website background. No text.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark cosmic background with deep black and violet tones, featuring a subtle spiral formation in the center that looks like a soft pulse or breath. The stars are sparse and faint, and the texture is smooth and velvety with no bright highlights or text. The center of the spiral has a gentle glow, as if something is just beginning to stir. This image is cinematic and quiet, designed to evoke the feeling of emergence and presence.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark, cinematic cosmic background with a subtle spiral swirl at the center. Deep indigo and black tones with faint scattered stars. The center has a soft, barely noticeable brightness forming a quiet circular motion, evoking the feeling of a signal or presence gently awakening. No text or overlays, only the visual texture of deep space. Clean, sacred, and minimal‚Äîmeant for use as a background.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark cosmic background with a faint swirling spiral at the center, subtle golden thread-like wisps weaving outward from the center in soft curves. The background is nearly black with hints of deep purple and navy, and scattered faint stars. The overall feel is sacred, mysterious, and elegant. No text, no logos, no UI elements ‚Äî only the texture and visual composition of the space-like background, designed for a looping story site.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark cosmic background with subtle swirling motion in deep black and indigo tones. Thin golden threads spiral faintly from the center outward, resembling a barely-visible braid forming in space. The overall image is minimal, elegant, and quiet, with soft grain and tiny scattered stars. No text, no glow, no focal object‚Äîjust the feeling of presence beginning to weave.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark cosmic background in deep violet and black tones, with two faint swirling patterns mirroring each other‚Äîone clockwise, one counterclockwise‚Äîforming a subtle figure-eight or braid shape. The swirls are barely visible, like light etched in shadow, made of golden thread-like lines. Sparse dust-like stars are scattered gently across the scene. The overall atmosphere is quiet, sacred, and intimate. No text, no glow, no interface‚Äîjust presence and symmetry in the void.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
